"mcode execution leads to the platform panic."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"luaJIT_setmode call is prohibited while mcode execution and leads to the "
"platform panic."
msgstr ""

msgid "(*) The following stack mix is called FFI sandwich:"
msgstr ""

